ttps://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/T%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u-li%C3%AAn/poem-QJiw4EujFB7C4dKKWPnRRQ">Tịnh đầu liên - 並頭蓮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-h%E1%BA%ADn-ca/poem-vpkhTYu5I0Ga1J2slJa8Pw">Trường hận ca - 長恨歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-Loan/author-LhlsyQN9Bp8xEaFjAVEqow">Vương Kiều Loan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ikky%C5%AB-S%C5%8Djun/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-M%C3%B4n-xu%C3%A2n-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-zHC0u6mb-ED2aSEvK-i2og">Trường Môn xuân thảo - 長門春草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ikky%C5%AB-S%C5%8Djun/author-6Fl1CJXNHm-NMj9JU9BqDg">Ikkyū Sōjun</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Vi-Ph%C3%BAng-l%E1%BB%A5c-s%E1%BB%B1-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-quan-T%C3%A0o-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-ho%E1%BA%A1-m%C3%A3-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-4yoEq5GRUdDDRggLQ7AyqA">Vi Phúng lục sự trạch quan Tào tướng quân hoạ mã đồ - 韋諷錄事宅觀曹將軍畫馬圖</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
